aring adamantite epaulets until level 60?  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/wink.gif"> Teehee.<P>But I remember Skrim slobbering to me about those silly shoulders about 20 levels ago--he deserves 'em. Grats again, my mentor!  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/wink.gif"><P></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
